            "question": "What if my parent's Social Security application is still pending?",
            "answer": "Your parent can apply for OAP while waiting for Social Security approval, but they must provide proof they've applied for Social Security and pursue that application. Once Social Security benefits start, the OAP amount will be reduced by the Social Security amount."
