      "intro": "Kentucky offers 2 key programs for family caregivers, ranging from comprehensive medical care coordination to support for grandparents raising grandchildren. These are qualification-based benefit programs that provide direct services and financial assistance if your situation meets specific criteria. Both programs focus on keeping families together and providing wraparound support rather than simple cash payments.",
